      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Natalie Scanlon, an International Hospitality and Tourism Management (Hons) student from Queen Margaret University (QMU), Edinburgh is one of five to receive an award of financial support from The Ryder Cup this year. Natalie, aged 19, was thrilled to be awarded a £1,000 bursary from Ryder Cup Europe.</p>]]></Value>
